{"tid":1473400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專門對台的老解恐嚇我地","createTime":"2019-08-14T23:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T23:43:07.000Z","uid":269304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e512f2eb853aa090e2a8c20908fac8678f48978","tid":1473400,"uid":269304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:43:07.000Z","msg":"有幾樣好心寒<br />\n<br />\n1.《基本法》指，香港一旦發生特區政府不能控制、危及國家統一或安全的動亂時，全國人大有權宣布特區進入緊急狀態，中央可發布命令，將有關全國性法律在香港實施<br />\n2.可以用《反恐法》追究香港組織<br />\n3. 駐港部隊可以參與防止動亂<br />\n4.深圳灣有五百輛軍車，十分鐘到港<br />\n5.關注此事的政府得德國同美國，西方對中國的制裁能力有限。<br />\n<br />\n有無熟悉國際法同法律的巴絲可以救救香港？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BC%E6%96%87-%E5%80%98%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D10%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-214500764.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2580%2598%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%2585%258B-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D10%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-214500764.html&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=24e54dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BC%E6%96%87-%E5%80%98%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D10%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-214500764.html</a>"}]}